cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR 

The paper presents a method for text classification using dimension reduction at the sequence level without labeled training data. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to machine learning and natural language processing. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are all possible sub-categories that could be relevant to this paper.
